				<wikidot:authorName>Khym Chanur</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>163438</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>SCP-2882 is capable of speaking in any language fluently, so long as it is first spoken to in the language. It is also competent at reading in any language but can only write in a language when instructed to.</p> </blockquote> <p>Seems like this would make him <em>way</em> too useful to the Foundation.</p> 
				 	]]>
