				<wikidot:authorName>RJ49</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1956342</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is pretty good. I read this as a draft and this definitely improved from it. I really got a feel of the SCP and the diary entries worked better thanks to the interview. The only thing that bothers me about this is how easily the Doctor was willing to give away such personal information to the SCP. I presume it had some kind of influence over her but that was never implied.</p> <p>Still this gets an upvote from me.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
